<link id="a1039" url="http://www.w3schools.com/js/default.asp">

http://www.w3schools.com/js/default.asp

</link>

). 
	(The purpose of this module is to help you gain that understanding.)

</item>


	

<item id="li1039">
An understanding of the creation and use of tactile graphics as 
	described
	

<link id="a1040" url="http://cnx.org/contents/9fe07552-485f-43e7-9753-87133cf60482">

here

</link>

.

</item>




</list>


	


